Estimated annual percentage change (EAPC) is a reliable method and widely used measure for describing the magnitude of the trends in ASDR [17, 20]. A regression line was fitted to the natural logarithm of the rates. The EAPC and its 95% confidence interval (CI) were calculated using the linear regression model, i.e.,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
